Base R 3D Plots

create 3d data using outer function

x <- 1:10
y <- 1:10

f <- outer(x, y, function(x,y) log(x)/1 + sin(x+y))


draw contour plot

useful for gradient descent

contour(x, y, f, nlevels = 25)


image plot

like a heatmap

image(x,y,f)


3d perspective plot

persp(x,y,f,
      theta = 230,
      phi = 45, 
      col = 'firebrick')
